These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: billiard, whist, canasta, scrabble
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, musical, western, mystery
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, snowmobile, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person driving the van is the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
5. the person watching musical movies is between the person driving the trike and the person playing whist##2
6. the person driving the snowmobile is the person watching western movies##1
7. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Game        | canasta | scrabble  | whist | billiard  |
| Movie-Genre         | mystery    | musical  | animation       | western     |
| Transport   | trike     | jet-ski | van       | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different games are played: billiard, domino, monopoly, canasta
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, sports, superhero, zombie
4 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse, chinchilla, hamster
1. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the hamster is between the person watching zombie movies and the person playing canasta##2
5. the person watching zombie movies is the owner of the mouse##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Game         | domino | billiard    | canasta  | monopoly |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | fantasy  | sports   | superhero    |
| Pet         | mouse | hamster | ferret | chinchilla      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, japanese, german, american
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, gardening, photography
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, zinnia, balloon-flower, lily
1. the person who growszinnia is between the person who growslily and the japanese##2
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the german is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
6. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Nationality      | japanese | american         | indonesian   | german    |
| Hobby         | cooking | photography | collecting | gardening |
| Flower   | balloon-flower   | zinnia        | lily      | poppy   |

