.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, whist, chess
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, november, june
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the ship and the person playing chess##2
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Game   | chess        | monopoly   | bridge | whist |
| Birthday         | november | april | december    | june |
| Transport     | scooter       | bus     | ship       | car    |

