4. the software-developer is on the left of the manager##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
6. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
7. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growsrose and the person who's hobby is gardening##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Job   | pilot | dancer      | software-developer       | manager   |
| Hobby      | gardening   | puzzles  | woodworking | sudoku     |
| Flower      | aconite     | poppy | rose        | zinnia |

