.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, techno, house, funk
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, fishing, gardening
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, brazilian, malaysian, nigerian
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the malaysian##1
3. the fan of trance is on the right of the pakistani##1
4. the nigerian is on the left of the fan of techno##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the malaysian##2
6. the fan of techno is between the fan of trance and the fan of house##2
7. the pakistani is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre    | house | techno  | trance | funk      |
| Hobby   | fishing  | gardening  | baking | collecting |
| Nationality   | nigerian | pakistani | brazilian | malaysian     |

