.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, airplane, skateboard, roller
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, epic, mystery, spy
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, light-blue, pink, coral
1. the person who likes coral is the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person who likes pink is the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
6. the person driving the airplane is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
7. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Transport          | skateboard  | airplane    | roller | jet-ski  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy       | epic        | drama    |
| Color         | light-blue | blood-red | coral  | pink |

