The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, funk, salsa, d&b
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, paramedic, social-worker, project-manager
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the software-developer##1
2. the fan of funk is between the project-manager and the person who's hobby is camping##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the social-worker##1
4. the social-worker is on the right of the software-developer##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku  | camping | cooking | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | country  | d&b | funk   | salsa         |
| Job           | software-developer | social-worker  | paramedic   | project-manager      |

