The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, zombie, romance, martial-arts
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, photography, woodworking, writing
House: townhouse, ranch-style, tower, colonial
1. the tower house is on the left of the colonial house##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the tower house and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
