.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, old-henry, prince, blend
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, tram, helicopter, snowmobile
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, time-travel
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is between the bluemaster-smoker and the person driving the tram##2
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is the person driving the snowmobile##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Cigar          | prince      | blend | old-henry | bluemaster |
| Transport         | snowmobile   | tram  | van | helicopter |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | adventure   | comedy | fantasy |

