.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, van, roller
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, puzzles, reading
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, soy-milk, coffee
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the roller##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person drinking coffee##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person drinking water##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Transport    | roller  | van | helicopter | quad-bike     |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles   | reading  | camping    |
| Beverage     | water        | coffee       | almond-milk      | soy-milk |

