The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, sudoku, traveling
There 4 different types of food: orange, pumpkin, cabbage, watermelon
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who likes ebony##1
3. the person who likes red is between the person who likes ebony and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes red is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
6. the person eating orange is on the far right##1
7. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Color   | pink | ebony     | red | ivory       |
| Hobby      | sudoku  | traveling | card-games  | gardening |
| Food        | watermelon  | pumpkin      | cabbage        | orange      |

