2. the person who growstulip is between the person drinking milk and the person traveling to new-york##2
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who growsmarigold##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
6. the person drinking water is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
