3. the turkish is the fan of metal##1
4. the australian is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the fan of salsa and the turkish##2
6. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
