The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, august, june, july
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, swimming, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's sport is swimming##2
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
7. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks    | board-games | woodworking           | camping |
| Birthday       | december | june    | august          | july   |
| Sport      | swimming  | rugby   | weightlifting | cricket  |

