.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, sudoku, hiking, photography
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, lavender, chestnut, red
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
5. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person who likes red is between the person drinking milk and the person who likes emerald##2
7. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | milk     | tea   |
| Hobby   | dancing | photography        | hiking  | sudoku  |
| Color           | emerald      | red         | lavender | chestnut |

