3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
4. the person eating corn is the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person eating corn##1
6. the person eating strawberry is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person eating corn##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate        | sprite  | juice | 7up   |
| Sport       | weightlifting | ice-hockey | surfing    | snowboarding |
| Food   | pear        | corn     | strawberry       | eggplant      |

