.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, water, lemonade
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, hamster, hedgehog
4 different games are played: poker, whist, backgammon, chess
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
5. the person playing chess is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the cat is between the person drinking lemonade and the person playing backgammon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage        | lemonade | fanta | tea | water |
| Pet         | bird       | cat     | hamster   | hedgehog   |
| Game   | poker | whist | backgammon | chess |

 